		<slash:comments>0</slash:comments>
<enclosure url="http://blip.tv/file/get/Culinarymedia-QuickBitesRiasBaixasValDoSalnes899.mp4" length="39134416" type="video/mp4" />
			<itunes:keywords>Albarino,Galicia,Marisol Bueno,Pazo de Senorans,Rias Baixas,Spain,winemakers</itunes:keywords>
		<itunes:subtitle>My tasting tour of Rias Baixas led to a wonderful discovery: The female winemakers in this region have made an indelible impression upon the quality of the wines and the respect AlbariÃ±o grapes have earned internationally.</itunes:subtitle>
		<itunes:summary>My tasting tour of Rias Baixas led to a wonderful discovery: The female winemakers in this region have made an indelible impression upon the quality of the wines and the respect AlbariÃ±o grapes have earned internationally.</itunes:summary>
