		<description><![CDATA[During our trip to Scotland, I sat down with Chef Jason Henderson from Knock Castle to talk about his approach to fine dining. I posted my initial impressions about Knock Castle, but this takes a little behind-the-scenes look at how Jason thinks about food, and what he wants people to experience in his dining room. [...]]]></description>
			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p></p><div class="tweetmeme_button" style="float: right; margin-left: 10px;">
			<a href="http://api.tweetmeme.com/share?url=http%3A%2F%2Ffoodphilosophy.com%2Ffp86-scottish-chef-jason-henderson%2F"><br />
				<img src="http://api.tweetmeme.com/imagebutton.gif?url=http%3A%2F%2Ffoodphilosophy.com%2Ffp86-scottish-chef-jason-henderson%2F&amp;source=foodphilosophy&amp;style=normal&amp;service=bit.ly&amp;b=2" height="61" width="50" /><br />
